msgid "基类"
msgstr "Base class"

#: ../../source/design/05-strategy-lifecycle.md
msgid "输入（get_data 等）"
msgstr "Inputs (get_data, etc.)"

#: ../../source/design/05-strategy-lifecycle.md
msgid "输出（realize 返回值）"
msgstr "Outputs (return value of realize)"

#: ../../source/design/05-strategy-lifecycle.md
msgid "典型用途"
msgstr "Typical use cases"

#: ../../source/design/05-strategy-lifecycle.md
msgid "**RuleIterator**"
msgstr "**RuleIterator**"

#: ../../source/design/05-strategy-lifecycle.md
msgid "单资产或多资产数据窗口，按 dtype_id 取"
msgstr "Single-asset or multi-asset data window, retrieved by dtype_id"

#: ../../source/design/05-strategy-lifecycle.md
msgid "标量（如 1/-1/0），同一规则迭代作用于所有资产"
msgstr "Scalar (e.g., 1/-1/0); the same rule iteration applies to all assets"

#: ../../source/design/05-strategy-lifecycle.md
msgid "择时、单规则多标的"
msgstr "Timing, single rule with multiple instruments"

#: ../../source/design/05-strategy-lifecycle.md
msgid "**FactorSorter**"
msgstr "**FactorSorter**"

#: ../../source/design/05-strategy-lifecycle.md
msgid "多资产截面（如每只股票的因子值）"
msgstr "Multi-asset cross section (e.g., factor values for each stock)"

#: ../../source/design/05-strategy-lifecycle.md
msgid "一维因子数组，引擎按排序与筛选规则选股"
msgstr ""
"A 1D factor array; the engine selects stocks according to ranking and filtering "
"rules"

#: ../../source/design/05-strategy-lifecycle.md
msgid "因子选股"
msgstr "Factor-based stock selection"

#: ../../source/design/05-strategy-lifecycle.md
msgid "**GeneralStg**"
msgstr "**GeneralStg**"

#: ../../source/design/05-strategy-lifecycle.md
msgid "多资产、多 dtype 的窗口"
msgstr "Multi-asset, multi-dtype windows"

#: ../../source/design/05-strategy-lifecycle.md
msgid "一维信号数组（每资产一个目标仓位或比例）"
msgstr "A 1D signal array (one target position or weight per asset)"

#: ../../source/design/05-strategy-lifecycle.md
msgid "通用多资产信号"
msgstr "General-purpose multi-asset signals"

#: ../../source/design/05-strategy-lifecycle.md:38
msgid "6. 小结"
msgstr "6. Summary"

#: ../../source/design/05-strategy-lifecycle.md:40
msgid ""
"同一套“按步 → 准备数据 → 注入 → realize() → 混合”的流程，同时服务回测与实盘：策"
"略不关心当前是回测还是实盘，只依赖 get_pars/get_data 与所属 Group 的时机；运行层"
"负责在不同模式下提供对应数据并处理输出信号。更多实现细节见《使用教程》与 API 参"
"考。"
msgstr ""
"The same “step → prepare data → inject → realize() → mix” workflow serves both "
"backtesting and live trading: the strategy does not care whether it is "
"currently backtesting or live; it only depends on get_pars/get_data and the "
"timing of its Group. The runtime layer is responsible for providing the "
"corresponding data in different modes and handling the output signals. For more "
"implementation details, see the “User Guide” and the API reference."
